The '''Lipartian Way''' was a street in [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]]. It was the location of a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] body shop that was much favored by [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]].

